    " \m  mark or unmark the word under (or before) the cursor  
    " \r  manually input a regular expression. .....  
    " \n  clear this mark (i.e. the mark under the cursor), or clear all highlighted marks .  
    " \*  ..MarkWord....     \#  ..MarkWord....  
    " \/  ..MarkWords....    \?  ..MarkWords....  
